    "rich_text_6ifKHD": {
      "type": "rich-text",
      "blocks": {
        "text_block_eeygQd": {
          "type": "text_block",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Sleeveless One Piece Swimsuits That Flatter, Sculpt, and Move With You",
            "title_heading": true,
            "accordion_enabled": true,
            "text": "<p>Effortless style meets high-performance design in our collection of sleeveless one piece swimsuits – made for women who want to feel confident, supported, and free to move. Whether you're swimming laps, freediving, paddleboarding, or simply soaking up the sun, these minimalist one pieces offer sleek support without restriction.<br/><br/>Crafted from premium recycled Italian fabric, each suit delivers a soft, second-skin feel while sculpting your shape with thoughtfully placed panels and a flattering cut. You won’t find bulky padding or flimsy straps here – just smart construction, double lining, and a fit that stays in place.</p><p>Our sleeveless swimsuits offer a blend of comfort, performance, and timeless style. They’re ideal for travel, water sports, or anyone looking for supportive one piece swimwear that feels amazing and lasts season after season.</p><p></p><p>Sculpting, sustainable, and surf-tested — these are one piece swimsuits you’ll want to wear everywhere.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "center": true,
            "block_width": 100,
            "accordion_icon_color": "#000000",
            "accordion_icon_size": 20
          }
        }
