    "image_with_text_YJVkPN": {
      "type": "image-with-text",
      "name": "Image with text",
      "settings": {
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/sil_such_Maldives1.jpg",
        "image_position": "left",
        "image_size": "medium",
        "image_height": "natural",
        "desktop_image_height": 350,
        "mobile_image_height": 450,
        "title": "",
        "text": "<h4>All-Day Comfort, Endless Confidence</h4><p>Sleeveless one pieces are the perfect blend of freedom and function. Our designs give you the movement of a bikini with the coverage and sculpting support of a one piece. </p><p>Ocean Soul's sleeveless one pieces are a favourite for:</p><p>Freedivers, surfers and swimmers who need full range of motion.<br/></p><p>Active women who want a no-fuss fit that moves with them.<br/></p><p>Mums and sun-seekers looking for sleek coverage without sleeves.</p>",
        "button_text": "Button",
        "link": "",
        "center_align": true,
        "text_color": "#606060",
        "background_color": "#f7f7f7"
      }
    },
    "image_with_text_3Hz4eX": {
      "type": "image-with-text",
      "name": "Image with text",
      "settings": {
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/Sleeveless_one_piece_swimsuit_in_Black.jpg",
        "image_position": "right",
        "image_size": "medium",
        "image_height": "natural",
        "desktop_image_height": 350,
        "mobile_image_height": 450,
        "title": "",
        "text": "<h4>Sustainable Swimwear That Performs</h4><p>Made from regenerated ECONYL® yarn, our swimsuits are crafted using ocean waste like fishing nets and fabric scraps, helping to reduce plastic pollution and support circular fashion. This eco-friendly swimwear feels incredibly soft while resisting chlorine, salt, and UV wear.</p><p>We double-line all our suits for durability and comfort, using no padding or foam. The support comes from expert tailoring and strong internal structure, not filler. The result? A swimsuit that lasts twice as long as standard swimwear and never loses its shape.</p><p></p>",
        "button_text": "Button",
        "link": "",
        "center_align": true,
        "text_color": "#606060",
        "background_color": "#ffffff"
      }
    },
    "image_with_text_aMMaPH": {
      "type": "image-with-text",
      "name": "Image with text",
      "settings": {
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/carssun_barbara_-_Ment_Nautical_-_2021-6_copy.jpg",
        "image_position": "left",
        "image_size": "medium",
        "image_height": "fixed",
        "desktop_image_height": 350,
        "mobile_image_height": 300,
        "title": "",
        "text": "<h4>Your Ideal Sleeveless One Piece </h4><p>If you're looking for a swimsuit that:</p><p>Flatters your body</p><p>Feels luxurious and soft</p><p>Performs in water-based sports</p><p>Protects your skin with UPF 50+ coverage</p><p>Aligns with your eco-conscious values</p><p>Ocean Soul's sleeveless swimsuits are more than just beautiful – they’re built for how you move, where you go, and how you want to feel. Supportive. Sculpted. Effortlessly elegant.</p>",
        "button_text": "Button",
        "link": "",
        "center_align": true,
        "text_color": "#606060",
        "background_color": "#f7f7f7"
      }
    },
