            "text": "<p>Look effortlessly chic in a sleeveless swimsuit designed for real life in and out of the water.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "center": true,
            "block_width": 100,
            "accordion_icon_color": "#000000",
            "accordion_icon_size": 20
          }
        },
        "text_block_e3akpp": {
          "type": "text_block",
          "settings": {
            "title": "",
            "title_heading": false,
            "accordion_enabled": false,
            "text": "<h3>Your Ideal Sleeveless One Piece Starts Here</h3><p>If you're looking for a swimsuit that:</p><p>Flatters your body</p><p>Feels luxurious and soft</p><p>Performs in water-based sports</p><p>Protects your skin with UPF 50+ coverage</p><p>Aligns with your eco-conscious values<br/><br/>… then this is the collection for you.</p><p>Ocean Soul's sleeveless swimsuits are more than just beautiful – they’re built for how you move, where you go, and how you want to feel. Supportive. Sculpted. Effortlessly elegant.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "center": true,
            "block_width": 100,
            "accordion_icon_color": "#000000",
            "accordion_icon_size": 20
          }
        },
        "text_block_A6kpEU": {
          "type": "text_block",
          "settings": {
            "title": "",
            "title_heading": false,
            "accordion_enabled": false,
            "text": "<p>Explore the<a href=\"/collections/sleeveless-one-piece-swimsuits\" title=\"Sleeveless One Piece Swimsuit Collection\"> collection </a>and find your new go-to one piece swimsuit today.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "center": true,
            "block_width": 100,
            "accordion_icon_color": "#000000",
            "accordion_icon_size": 20
          }
        }
      },
